#X text 316 312 set threshold;
#X text 18 49 soft limiter based on a tangent function - adjustable
threshold [0 \, 1] lets through signal below the threshold perfectly
clean and puts signal above the threshold through a tangent curve in
order to scale it down: 1 is a simple hard limiter \, 0 is a plain
tangent function.;
